      • findField

        public TiffOutputField findField(TagInfo tagInfo)
        Finds the TiffOutputField for the given TagInfo from this TiffOutputDirectory.

        If there is no field matching the given TagInfo, null will be returned.

        Parameters:
        tagInfo - the TagInfo specifying the field
        Returns:
        the field matching tagInfo or null, if the field isn't present
        See Also:
        findField(int)
